<subSubSection pageId="69" pageNumber="70" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="69.[151,1437,1230,1797]" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">
REMARKS: 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[270,511,1519,1545]" pageId="69" pageNumber="70" pagination="63 - 112" refId="ref368107" refString="Rondani, C. (1848 b) Esame di varie specie d'insetti ditteri brasiliani. Studi Entomologici, 1 (1), 63 - 112, pl. IIIbis." type="journal article" year="1848">Rondani (1848b: 98)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<emphasis box="[640,870,1519,1545]" italics="true" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1848" box="[640,866,1519,1545]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Toxophora" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="69" pageNumber="70" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aurifera">Toxophora aurifera</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
without specifying either the 
<taxonomicName box="[1224,1310,1519,1545]" family="Number" pageId="69" pageNumber="26" rank="family">number</taxonomicName>
or the sex of the specimens, but giving a single measurement of length, from material collected in South America by V. Ghiliani and received from G. Mussino. 
<bibRefCitation author="Costa, A." box="[653,841,1591,1617]" pageId="69" pageNumber="70" pagination="13 - 48" refId="ref348459" refString="Costa, A. (1866) Acquisti fatti durante l'anno 1863. Annuario del Museo Zoologico della Regia Universita di Napoli, 3, 13 - 48." type="journal article" year="1866">Costa (1866: 37)</bibRefCitation>
listed a single MZUN specimen (as 
<taxonomicName authority="Phil." authorityName="Phil." class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Texophora" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="69" pageNumber="70" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aurifera">
<emphasis box="[1251,1370,1591,1617]" italics="true" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">Texophora</emphasis>
[
<emphasis box="[1386,1417,1591,1616]" italics="true" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">sic</emphasis>
!] 
<emphasis box="[199,291,1627,1653]" italics="true" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">aurifera</emphasis>
Phil.
</taxonomicName>
) numbered “853”. 
<bibRefCitation author="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Greathead, D. J." box="[570,953,1627,1653]" pageId="69" pageNumber="70" refId="ref349891" refString="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Greathead, D. J. (1999) World catalog of bee flies (Diptera: Bombyliidae). Backhuys Publishers, Leiden, 756 pp." type="book" year="1999">Evenhuis &amp; Greathead (1999: 70)</bibRefCitation>
reported the specimen in the MZUN to be a 
<typeStatus box="[219,321,1663,1689]" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">holotype</typeStatus>
. Although 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[442,675,1663,1690]" pageId="69" pageNumber="70" pagination="63 - 112" refId="ref368107" refString="Rondani, C. (1848 b) Esame di varie specie d'insetti ditteri brasiliani. Studi Entomologici, 1 (1), 63 - 112, pl. IIIbis." type="journal article" year="1848">Rondani (1848b: 63)</bibRefCitation>
only gave the type locality as “ 
<collectingCountry box="[1026,1112,1663,1689]" name="Brazil" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">Brasile</collectingCountry>
”, 
<bibRefCitation author="Papavero, N." box="[1134,1376,1663,1689]" pageId="69" pageNumber="70" refId="ref362581" refString="Papavero, N. (1973) Essays on the history of Neotropical dipterology, with special reference to collectors (1750 - 1905). Vol. 2. Museu de Zoologia, Universidade de Sao Paolo, Sao Paolo, pp. 217 - 446." type="book" year="1973">Papavero (1973: 343)</bibRefCitation>
gave a more accurate type locality based on a note in 
<bibRefCitation author="Spinola, M." box="[755,923,1698,1725]" pageId="69" pageNumber="70" pagination="19 - 94" refId="ref374743" refString="Spinola, M. (1853) Compte rendu des hymenopteres inedits provenants du voyage entomologique de M. Ghiliani dans le Para en 1846. Memorie della Reale Accademia delle Scienze di Torino, Series 2, 13, 19 - 94." type="journal article" year="1853">Spinola (1853)</bibRefCitation>
that said all specimens collected by Ghiliani in 1846 were collected in Belem, Pará, 
<collectingCountry box="[644,716,1735,1761]" name="Brazil" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">Brazil</collectingCountry>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Greathead, D. J." box="[727,1109,1735,1761]" pageId="69" pageNumber="70" refId="ref349891" refString="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Greathead, D. J. (1999) World catalog of bee flies (Diptera: Bombyliidae). Backhuys Publishers, Leiden, 756 pp." type="book" year="1999">Evenhuis &amp; Greathead (1999: 70)</bibRefCitation>
reported the specimen in the MZUN to be a 
<typeStatus box="[370,472,1771,1797]" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">holotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
